Description: Jellyfin media server management
 SecuBox module for managing Jellyfin media server via Docker.
 Provides container management, library configuration,
 backup/restore, and hardware acceleration support.
 .
 Ported from OpenWRT luci-app-jellyfin.
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/jellyfin/ via Unix socket.
